main event: A UFO sighting was reported on January 28, 1962, in Bethel, Alaska, involving an object that seemed to maneuver like a craft with multiple lights.
interesting points: The object was estimated to be 25 to 30 feet in size,The object emitted no sound and had no visible exhaust,The sighting lasted about 5 minutes before the object disappeared,The observer was a 33-year-old auto mechanic, considered very reliable,There are no physical evidence or photographs presented in the report.
sighted object: an object similar to an aircraft with multiple lights
